                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-09-29</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I could not put this book down. All Edward Abbey lovers will be enchanted with this book. Those of you that skip it are missing out on an all time treasure. This book is an excellent way to distract yourself from the World Trade Center disaster.</span>
                  
              
